  "keyFeatures": [
    "Hot-swappable device backends with automatic hardware detection",
    "Native support for AI agents and multi-agent systems",
    "Comprehensive reinforcement learning algorithms (DQN, PPO, SAC, etc.)",
    "Distributed training with MPI, Horovod, and DeepSpeed",
    "Edge-optimized deployment with quantization and pruning",
    "Graph Neural Networks and advanced architectures",
    "Federated learning with secure aggregation",
    "AutoML and neural architecture search",
    "Quantum computing integration (Qiskit, Cirq)",
    "Multi-backend hardware acceleration (CUDA, ROCm, Vulkan, ARM, TPU)",
    "ONNX model import/export",
    "API serving with REST, WebSocket, and gRPC",
    "Continual learning and lifelong training",
    "Explainable AI with SHAP and LIME",
    "Neuroevolution and evolutionary algorithms"
